Here’s what I’m experimenting with at the moment. Any input is welcome:
```.span12.dnd-column &gt; .dnd-row &gt; .row-fluid {
  max-width:1170px;
  box-sizing: content-box;
  margin:0 auto;
  padding:0 7%;
  display:grid !important;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(12,1fr);
  grid-gap:5rem;
}

